messages.msgSnippet: I got an e-mail called What s Up With Kirby This Saturday? and I opened it!  It was a good question.  He has a really complicated schedule today--went to work
messages.messageBody:
I got an e-mail called
What's Up With Kirby This Saturday?
and I opened it! It was a good question. He has a really complicated
schedule today--went to work at 8:30, will be at the last 1/3 of Holly's
birthday party, and then is going to a birthday party at a house where he's
never been, invited by a girl in his karate class.

But it wasn't about MY Kirby, it was about that pink Nintendo Kirby. But I
read on some anyway:

Take The Kirby Kwiz!



Question: Which of the following are NOT modes

into which Kirby can transform?



Needle Kirby

Ninja Kirby

Tornado Kirby

Sword Kirby

Thunder Kirby

Microphone Kirby

Stone Kirby

Ice Kirby

If those, I've never seen Kirby Dodd by Needle Kirby, Microphone Kirby, or
Stone Kirby. I've seen all the rest myself in person. <bwg>
